<subSubSection id="AD02C8D6AEE7F263AE0AF5269D660340" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="644255ADC9E8ED95A11B749CC0CE1133" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Bremis Wasserschlauch</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="7F31D8383C2EBA5DF786A97C8088344B" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" type="description">
<paragraph id="60D0C28A159EEF67EA47C9AA30E43E38" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
Pflanze im Habitus wie 
<taxonomicName id="65C607643C170A16DC102DBF331014DA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lentibulariaceae" genus="Utricularia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minor">
<emphasis id="C49B3DA3C590C34F97F1F444F50864DA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">U. minor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3), jedoch in allen Teilen 
<normalizedToken id="4B67A78359839CCB065093ADF40F204F" originalValue="größer" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">groesser</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="AE8E5904EE6DD6065C8AAA78681779C8" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<emphasis id="2780031C555CEC5C4ABD0B47EFA0043A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
<taxonomicName id="55A53B968AC105E8D28C38ED2CFE60B4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lentibulariaceae" genus="Utricularia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minor">U. minor</taxonomicName>
; Abschnitte aber oft 4
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="AEDB73C6B1052B3040E144BDC70C6AE9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">5mal gabelig geteilt.</emphasis>
Stengel, 
<normalizedToken id="502E3263EE97FFBB3BFB4784A8AE25DA" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="AABD8F43266BBE19F6507C11ABC5C23A" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="5BEF61C1A72F97F65E13582A155AF858" authority="Kronblaetter" authorityName="Kronblaetter" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lentibulariaceae" genus="Utricularia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minor">
<emphasis id="7B650D007AA03F429058DF526A3297AB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">U. minor</emphasis>
<pageBreakToken id="CC4D5764F3C84990EE35D0C42C109E40" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
<normalizedToken id="8B0C44EE78145321F15B407D015062B5" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
</pageBreakToken>
</taxonomicName>
hellgelb; 
<emphasis id="035D7E4D4480435544F8A145A1A45B76" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
Oberlippe oval, so lang oder 
<normalizedToken id="B65368D11D59D866B6E94404A424D66A" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">laenger</normalizedToken>
als der Gaumen der Unterlippe; Unterlippe rundlich
</emphasis>
, im Durchmesser 8-9 mm, 
<emphasis id="9AEFB5A46C42ACB34C82D6E4F3ED844D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">flach ausgebreitet;</emphasis>
Sporn wie bei 
<emphasis id="EF25D8E14D813BF425857CF942081353" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
<taxonomicName id="228C8B7372CC0B1EDF00AD7C445B34E9" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lentibulariaceae" genus="Utricularia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minor">U. minor</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="9F1234DB8F0BF9DED72427D9F2C75296" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
kugelig, selten. - 
<normalizedToken id="9768DC4233CDF0E50A65F0083CD9E667" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer bis Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8E150A72A66B9467415C7502E38BE35E" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
<emphasis id="FB45D89F380F5E98EE4DB9493C0DDAC9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="52D84222191E8A01684593C7A1A39388" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
<emphasis id="AF4BB18075B97FED2923E58D45E5989E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="9166AB6BE658135A5319EF2AE01DDC92" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lentibulariaceae" genus="Utricularia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intermedia">
<emphasis id="77DC6C92E4A8AD28096CC69E7577EF7E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">U. intermedia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5); noch wenig untersucht.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8D4F496E0242B26617784D3915356DD4" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
<emphasis id="4E4EA16613D5DA0BF850EACEED3C3E38" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="D44B40ED60D2DB6C906FC2148C8FECF1" originalValue="Europäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Europaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Ist aus dem Mediterrangebiet, den Balkanstaaten, Schweden und Finnland nicht bekannt. - Im Gebiet selten: 
<normalizedToken id="65A520842CD3DB44D258082D8298F3D2" originalValue="Elsaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Elsass</normalizedToken>
(zwischen Neudorf und Rosenau), 
<normalizedToken id="063E88B19D2C411D1626A78FCB52059D" originalValue="Zürich" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">Zuerich</normalizedToken>
(Katzensee), Gegend von Varese, Wallis (Crans, Scierie de Lens [ist 
<normalizedToken id="0738C56312662B6923565CE1A1BA8445" originalValue="nachzuprüfen" pageId="null" pageNumber="268">nachzupruefen</normalizedToken>
]).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
